version 0.2:
	* improve plotTopDensities & friends: no more automatic sorting
          by score. It's actually much more flexible to let the user
	  specify the preferred ordering
	* improve barplots utilities man pages
	* add some more cross-references
	* improve Compose func: now uses 'match.fun'
	* add plotTopMosaics func
	* add fisherCorrelation func for evaluating association
	  between categorical variables
	* add plotTopJitters & friends plotting functions
	* add 'xlim' option to plotTopDensities, with sensible default
	* add 'rug' option to plotTopDensities
	* add plotMixDensity: more flexible w.r.t. plotTopDensities
 	  (which uses it)
	* add utility bimodalityScore and bimodalityFilter functions
	* add ability to compute multiple indexes at once, without
	  refitting the mixture

version 0.1: 21/05/2010

